OL,3,CGuernsey doctors told to phase out
OL,4,Cpain relief plasters
OL,6,FDoctors in have been told to "stop or
OL,7,Fgreatly reduce" prescribing lidocaine
OL,8,Fplasters.
OL,10,FOver the last 12 months #100,000 was
OL,11,Fspent on these plasters, which are
OL,12,Ftypically used to relieve nerve pain
OL,13,Fin adults after a shingles infection.
OL,15,FThe measure forms part of the States'
OL,16,Fongoing evaluation into the cost of
OL,17,Fmedicines provided at tax payer's
OL,18,Fexpense.
