OL,3,CGuernsey doctors told to phase out
OL,4,Cpain relief plasters
OL,6,FMany of those currently prescribed
OL,7,Flidocaine plasters should have already
OL,8,Fhad their treatment reviewed.
OL,10,FIf not, patients are encouraged to
OL,11,Fconsult their doctor to explore
OL,12,Falternative forms of pain relief.
OL,14,FThe Committee for Health & Social Care
OL,15,Fhave said that this cost-cutting
OL,16,Fpolicy will help to fund the
OL,17,F"significant number of new treatments"
OL,18,Favailable to islanders.
